    { title: "Apply security reviews to capabilities before adoption", content: "When a new AI capability becomes available to your organization (computer use, multi-agent coordination, longer autonomy), conduct a structured security review before deploying it. Ask: what new attack surfaces does this create? What existing controls break? What new controls are needed?", icon: "🔍" },
    { title: "Engage with standards bodies and industry groups", content: "NIST, CISA, ISO, and sector-specific bodies are developing AI security standards now. Participating in these efforts means your organization's experience shapes the standards — and you get early warning of regulatory direction.", icon: "🤝" },
